OL,3,CGraham Linehan's trans activist posts
OL,4,Cwere 'oppressive', court told
OL,6,FFather Ted creator Graham Linehan's
OL,7,Fposts about a transgender activist
OL,8,Fwere "oppressive" and "vindictive," a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.
OL,11,FThe 57-year-old Irish comedy writer
OL,12,Fappeared at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt on Thursday, accused of
OL,14,Fharassing transgender activist Sophia
OL,15,FBrooks.
