OL,3,CGraham Linehan's trans activist posts
OL,4,Cwere 'oppressive', court told
OL,6,FLinehan has denied one count of
OL,7,Fharassing the activist on social media
OL,8,Fbetween October 11 and October 27 last
OL,9,Fyear, as well as a further charge of
OL,10,Fcriminal damage to her mobile phone on
OL,11,FOctober 19 last year.
OL,13,FProsecutor Julia Faure Walker said
OL,14,FLinehan posted about the activist
OL,15,F"relentlessly".
OL,17,FShe said: "These posts were not merely
OL,18,Firritating or annoying, but rather
OL,19,Foppressive and unacceptable, thereby
OL,20,Fcrossing the threshold into harassment.
