OL,3,CGraham Linehan's trans activist posts
OL,4,Cwere 'oppressive', court told
OL,6,F"These posts were not provoked by Ms
OL,7,FBrooks online in respect of anything
OL,8,Fshe had done to Graham Linehan."
OL,10,FMs Faure Walker added: "The purpose of
OL,11,Fthe posts was clearly not merely to
OL,12,Frelay events, to express political
OL,13,Fopinion, to criticise, to help
OL,14,Fidentify perpetrators, or to try to
OL,15,Fsolve any crime.
OL,17,F"Nor is it a case that these posts
OL,18,Fmerely presented ideas that may shock,
OL,19,Fdisturb, or offend.
